<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Welcome to LETFs Data Validator</title>
    <style>
        * {
            font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
        }

        table {
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
        }

        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 16px
        }

        h2 {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 12px
        }

        td, th {
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            padding: 8px;
        }

        tr:nth-child(even) {
            background-color: #f2f2f2;
        }

        tr:hover {
            background-color: #ddd;
        }

        th {
            padding-top: 12px;
            padding-bottom: 12px;
            text-align: left;
            background-color: #04AA6D;
            color: white;
        }

        /*TODO: Align the css better*/
        .letf_ticker {
            padding: 2px 2px;
            margin: 2px 5px;
            border: 1px solid;
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            background-position: 10px center;
            border-radius: 3px;
            /*display: block;*/
            color: #8bd3fa;
            background-color: #bcbcbc;
        }

        #bottom {
            background-color: #04AA6D;
            padding: 50px;
            margin-top: 200px;
        }

        #bottom_table {
            color: white;
        }

        #bottom_table > tr:hover {
            background-color: #04AA6D;
        }

        a:link {
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        a:visited {
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        a:hover {
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        a:active {
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<h1>Abstract</h1>
<p>
    The goal of this project is to simplify LETF exploration. Just a fun project in spare time.<br/>
    We found {{ .TotalProvider }} providers, {{ .TotalSeeds }} seeds
</p>
<table>
    <tr>
        <th>Provider</th>
        <th>Count</th>
        <th>LETFs</th>
    </tr>
    {{ with .Providers }}
    {{ range $key, $value := . }}
    <tr>
        <td>{{ $key }}</td>
        <td>{{len $value }}</td>
        <td>
            {{ range $ticker, $value := . }}
            <span class="letf_ticker"><a href="summary/{{ $ticker }}.html">{{ $ticker }}</a></span>
            {{ end }}
        </td>
    </tr>
    {{ end }}
    {{ end }}
</table>
<div id="bottom">
    <table id="bottom_table">
        <tr>
            <td>
                Powered by GitHub
            </td>
            <td>
                Powered by GCP
            </td>
            <td>
                Please file issues, features <a href="https://github.com/ravivooda/stocks/issues/new/choose">here</a>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</div>
</body>
</html>